name: Everydaykannadastories
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: everyday kannada stories
des:
This skill is build for children below 5 years. Alexa will tell them a story in kannada language, which will help them to easily understand.
It will tell the small stories which are less than 5 minutes. 
It will ask them the questions regarding the story to make it more interactive.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
